## tool-session-model-reset: session, model, and reset tool definitions

### session(action: str, session_id: str = "") -> str
Manage agent sessions.
- action="list"   -- list all active sessions with their IDs, model, and history size.
- action="delete" -- delete a session by ID (shorthand integer or full session ID).

### model(action: str, model_key: str = "") -> str
Manage the active LLM model for this session.
- action="list" -- show all available models (current model marked).
- action="set"  -- switch to the named model (model_key required).

### reset() -> str
Clear conversation history for the current session.
